# HR Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project is an HR Analytics Dashboard developed using Power BI to analyze employee attrition, workforce demographics, job satisfaction, and department performance.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Microsoft Excel
- Power Query
- DAX

