![HR Dashboard](Screenshot%202026-06-01%20094948.png)

## Key Insights
- Employee Attrition Analysis
- Department-wise Employee Distribution
- Job Satisfaction Tracking
- Employee Demographics Analysis
- Workforce Performance Metrics

